headline: Dell Technologies Accelerates Enterprise AI Innovation from PC to Data Center with NVIDIA
summary: SAN JOSE, Calif., March 18, 2025--NVIDIA GTC 2025: Marking one year since the launch of the Dell AI Factory with NVIDIA, Dell Technologies (NYSE: DELL) announces new AI PCs, infrastructure, software and services advancements to accelerate enterprise AI innovation at any scale.
